{"title":"刷墙","authors":["李金平"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刷墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李金平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条斑驳的标语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一条僵死的蛇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栖息在砖缝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月的风雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有冲去狂热的阴影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，我选择了一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晴朗的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用滴翠的油彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新粉刷这段墙壁——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新粉刷这段历史；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片春天的绿荫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在墙壁上扩散、蔓延，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熄灭了点点残存的火星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗅着芳香的油彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然生活还有死角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有侥幸的幻梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要挥动春天的刷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉刷一切疏忽和漏洞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给未来的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂上一片安宁。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}